title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell
OB: An exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method when attempting to export data in a table that is inside a grid cell.
EB: When exporting data in two tables, the expected result is that the data should be exported successfully without any exceptions.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Insert one table into one grid cell. 2. Insert another table into the other grid cell.
